00:14:25.010 --> 00:14:26.940 align:middle line:90%
and you're not hiking around.

00:14:26.940 --> 00:14:31.200 align:middle line:84%
But you're there, and you have
nothing to do except tune in.

00:14:31.200 --> 00:14:34.520 align:middle line:84%
No television, no reading,
nothing to distract you.

00:14:34.520 --> 00:14:40.865 align:middle line:84%
And I you spend a lot of
time watching the weather

00:14:40.865 --> 00:14:42.990 align:middle line:84%
and thinking, oh, where
