00:14:45.815 --> 00:14:47.900 align:middle line:90%
and all of that kind of thing.

00:14:47.900 --> 00:14:50.300 align:middle line:84%
And taking precautions--
building a shelter,

00:14:50.300 --> 00:14:52.510 align:middle line:90%
building a fire.

