00:15:18.770 --> 00:15:21.260 align:middle line:90%
and minimum inconvenience.

00:15:21.260 --> 00:15:26.180 align:middle line:84%
And yet at the cost of really
shutting off our perception

00:15:26.180 --> 00:15:27.740 align:middle line:90%
and not observing.

00:15:27.740 --> 00:15:32.300 align:middle line:84%
And the ever-changing patterns
