00:15:32.300 --> 00:15:35.930 align:middle line:84%
So being alone on a vision
quest in the wilderness

00:15:35.930 --> 00:15:39.410 align:middle line:84%
is an ancient tradition
of native North American

00:15:39.410 --> 00:15:43.280 align:middle line:84%
Indians and other societies,
