00:15:43.280 --> 00:15:45.710 align:middle line:84%
alone by yourself, and
you pray for a vision,

00:15:45.710 --> 00:15:49.900 align:middle line:84%
which is a vision meaning a
sort of guidance for your life.

00:15:49.900 --> 00:15:53.010 align:middle line:84%
What am I supposed
to do with my life?

00:15:53.010 --> 00:15:53.810 align:middle line:90%
Where am I going?

00:15:53.810 --> 00:15:56.600 align:middle line:90%
What's my role in life?

00:15:56.600 --> 00:16:00.260 align:middle line:84%
And maybe the person
who is on a vision

00:16:00.260 --> 00:16:02.330 align:middle line:84%
quest will connect with
spirits of animals,

00:16:02.330 --> 00:16:03.980 align:middle line:84%
and then they might
become a healer,

00:16:03.980 --> 00:16:07.550 align:middle line:84%
or they might become an artist,
or whatever their role may be.

00:16:07.550 --> 00:16:10.160 align:middle line:84%
And people have done
this traditionally

00:16:10.160 --> 00:16:13.200 align:middle line:84%
at certain key transition
points in their life,

00:16:13.200 --> 00:16:17.180 align:middle line:84%
particularly adolescence, in
the kind of rite of passage

00:16:17.180 --> 00:16:21.540 align:middle line:84%
for helping a young person move
out of the matrix of the family

00:16:21.540 --> 00:16:24.870 align:middle line:84%
into a larger matrix of
society and define themselves

00:16:24.870 --> 00:16:27.810 align:middle line:84%
as a member of that
tribe or society

00:16:27.810 --> 00:16:31.020 align:middle line:84%
and find their position
