00:16:31.020 --> 00:16:33.800 align:middle line:84%
But now people are
doing the vision quests

00:16:33.800 --> 00:16:35.680 align:middle line:90%
at any kind of transition--

00:16:35.680 --> 00:16:37.770 align:middle line:84%
work, midlife transition,
work transition,

00:16:37.770 --> 00:16:42.300 align:middle line:84%
relationship transitions, or
crisis, that kind of thing,

00:16:42.300 --> 00:16:44.390 align:middle line:90%
finding themselves in a new way.

00:16:44.390 --> 00:16:48.270 align:middle line:84%
It can be done
outside in nature,

00:16:48.270 --> 00:16:50.820 align:middle line:84%
or it can be done-- some
do it through meditation.

00:16:50.820 --> 00:16:54.270 align:middle line:84%
Some do it through visionary
substances or plants,

00:16:54.270 --> 00:16:56.030 align:middle line:84%
shamanic practices
of various kinds.

00:16:56.030 --> 00:16:57.570 align:middle line:90%
And sometimes it just comes.

00:16:57.570 --> 00:17:01.740 align:middle line:84%
But the role of intention
