00:17:13.800 --> 00:17:16.829 align:middle line:84%
You have to intend
it so that you

00:17:16.829 --> 00:17:19.390 align:middle line:90%
would look in that direction.

00:17:19.390 --> 00:17:22.290 align:middle line:84%
