00:18:11.280 --> 00:18:14.500 align:middle line:84%
the vacuum of space is
alive and conscious.

00:18:14.500 --> 00:18:15.300 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:18:15.300 --> 00:18:20.040 align:middle line:84%
