further extension of that.

00:18:20.040 --> 00:18:26.880 align:middle line:84%
So Lovelock said the atmosphere
is part of the organism of Gaia

00:18:26.880 --> 00:18:29.220 align:middle line:90%
just like the shell of a snail.

00:18:29.220 --> 00:18:32.010 align:middle line:84%
In fact, very
analogous to the shell

00:18:32.010 --> 00:18:34.560 align:middle line:90%
