actually produced by life.

00:18:36.930 --> 00:18:39.340 align:middle line:84%
It's an outgassing of
life, organic life.

00:18:39.340 --> 00:18:40.140 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:18:40.140 --> 00:18:43.710 align:middle line:84%
>> And that's why you don't have
an atmosphere in outer space,

00:18:43.710 --> 00:18:45.310 align:middle line:90%
