00:18:45.310 --> 00:18:48.990 align:middle line:84%
And it's maintained by life
just in the right conditions

00:18:48.990 --> 00:18:50.700 align:middle line:84%
and temperature and
chemical composition

00:18:50.700 --> 00:18:52.360 align:middle line:84%
to be favorable
for even more life.

00:18:52.360 --> 00:18:54.485 align:middle line:84%
So that's what makes
