00:19:43.563 --> 00:19:45.980 align:middle line:84%
You couldn't have the parts
be conscious and not the whole

00:19:45.980 --> 00:19:46.600 align:middle line:90%
be conscious.

00:19:46.600 --> 00:19:48.350 align:middle line:84%
